    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo, featuring the iconic 2JZ-GTE 3.0L twin-turbocharged inline-six engine. This example is mated to the original Getrag V160 6-speed manual gearbox, delivering power through a factory Torsen limited-slip differential. The vehicle remains in pristine, unmodified configuration, retaining its stock sequential turbocharger setup and four-wheel double-wishbone suspension. With all original VIN tags present and the factory four-piston brake calipers showing zero fade, this chassis represents the zenith of JDM performance engineering. A turn-key investment for the discerning enthusiast seeking an analog driving experience in flawless mechanical order.",
