      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to acquire a true time capsule. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, retaining its original showroom-floor luster. The exterior paint is deep, vibrant, and entirely free of swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings. Every body panel aligns with factory precision, and the glass and trim remain in flawless condition. Inside, the cabin is a masterclass in preservation; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of wear, the bolsters are firm, and the carpets are immaculate. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the climate control, functions perfectly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It has been serviced exclusively by certified technicians using OEM parts, with a complete log of all preventative maintenance. The engine bay is detailed to a mirror finish, and the undercarriage is as clean as the top. This is not just a used car; it is a museum-quality example that drives with the same tightness and responsiveness as the day it was delivered. For the discerning collector who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
